data.description: *Qualifies for a discounted interest rate* Flier in documents. Wonderful home in a highly sought after area in Crowley. This 2016 model home has an open floor plan. The kitchen has a wall of cabinets that have great storage and a separate pantry. Split bedrooms for privacy. Wonderful natural lighting in the living room and breakfast area. Tile in the bathrooms with granite counter tops, large walk in shower and closet, upgraded faucets and fixtures. The mud room has a bench and shelves. Great sized covered patio with an oversized yard. The fridge and storage shed in the back yard are included.
